  "title": "M & E Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To prepare and submit materials and shop drawings to consultants for approval.</li>\n  <li>To control and coordinate M&amp;E Works on site</li>\n  <li>To resolve site matters with regards to M&amp;E services</li>\n  <li>To manage sub-contractors works and progress of works</li>\n  <li>To liaise with authorities for the commission of work</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Passed M&amp;E coordination course.</li>\n  <li>Possess at least 2-3 years of relevant working experience in M&amp;E industry</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in Microsoft office (Word &amp; Excel), Microsoft Project and AutoCAD.</li>\n  <li>All are welcome to apply.</li>\n</ul>",
